<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head class="no-js">
	<title>Smith &amp; Robot</title>

	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
	<%- @getBlock('meta').toHTML(); %>
	<%- @getBlock('styles').toHTML(); %>

	<script src="http://use.typekit.net/unl8vyi.js"></script>
	<script>try{Typekit.load();}catch(e){}</script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="l-pageContainer">
		<header role="banner">
			<div class="grid">
				<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-10-12-medium grid-push-1-12-medium l-positionContext">
					<div class="grid">
						<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-1-4-medium text-center text-left-medium">
							<img src="/images/logo.png" width="150" />
						</div>
						<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-3-4-medium">
							<nav>
								<ul id="SectionMenu" class="menu menu--horizontal menuSkin--sections">
									<li class="menu-item" data-target="#123">
										<span>About</span>
									</li><li class="menu-item" data-target="#124">
										<span>Contact</span>
									</li>
								</ul>
							</nav>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</header>

		<div class="sectionPanes">
			<div class="grid">
				<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-10-12-medium grid-push-1-12-medium">
					<article class="contentPane" id="123">
						<div class="hr"></div>
						<div class="contentPane-closeButton"><img src="/images/close.png" width="28" /></div>
						<h1>Digital First</h1>

						<div class="grid">
							<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-4-10-medium">
								<p>Morbi leo risus, porta ac consectetur ac, vestibulum at eros. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Nulla vitae elit libero, a pharetra augue. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Donec sed odio dui.</p>
								<p>Cras mattis consectetur purus sit amet fermentum. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-3-10-medium">
								<img src="/images/chad-currie-smith-and-robot.jpg" width="100%" class="blockElement" />
								<p><span class="textUrgent">Chad Currie</span><span class="textImportant">, Creative Director.</span> Morbi leo risus, porta ac consectetur ac, vestibulum at eros. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Nulla <a href="#">vitae elit libero</a>, a pharetra augue. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Donec sed odio dui.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-3-10-medium">
								<img src="/images/david-ford-smith-and-robot.jpg" width="100%" class="blockElement" />
								<p><span class="textUrgent">David Ford</span><span class="textImportant">, Technology Director.</span> Morbi leo risus, porta ac consectetur ac, vestibulum at eros. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Nulla <a href="#1">vitae elit libero</a>, a pharetra augue. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Donec sed odio dui.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</article>

					<article class="contentPane" id="124">
						<div class="hr"></div>
						<div class="contentPane-closeButton"><img src="/images/close.png" width="28" /></div>
						<h1>Ready to Listen</h1>

						<div class="grid">
							<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-1-2-medium">
								<form>
									<p>
										<label for="emailField" class="visuallyHidden">Your Email Address</label>
										<input type="email" placeholder="Your Email Address" name="email" id="emailField" class="blockElement" />
									</p>

									<p>
										<label for="messageField" class="visuallyHidden">Your Message</label>
										<textarea name="message" id="messageField" placeholder="Your Message" class="blockElement" ></textarea>
									</p>

									<p>
										<input type="submit" value="Send Message" class="btn btnSkinPrimary blockElement" />
									</p>
								</form>
							</div>
							<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-1-2-medium">
								<p>
									<a href="http://maps.google.com"><img src="/images/staticmap.png" width="100%"></a><br/>

									Smith &amp; Robot, LLC<br/>
									3410 Far West Blvd, Suite 301<br/>
									Austin, Texas 78731<br/>
									1 (512) 696-0418<br/>
								</p>

								<p>
									<img src="images/icons/email.png" width="16" class="inlineIcon" />://<a href="mailto:introductions@smithandrobot.com">introductions@smithandrobot.com</a><br/>
									<img src="images/icons/twitter.png" width="16" class="inlineIcon" />://<a href="https://twitter.com/smithandrobot">@smithandrobot</a><br/>
									<img src="images/icons/facebook.png" width="16" class="inlineIcon" />://<a href="https://www.facebook.com/Smith.Robot">Smith.Robot</a><br/>
									<img src="images/icons/linkedin.png" width="16" class="inlineIcon" />://<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/company/smith-&amp;-robot_2">smith-&amp;-robot_2</a>
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<article class="contentPane">
			<div class="grid">
				<div class="grid-cell-1-1 grid-cell-10-12-medium grid-push-1-12-medium">
					<div class="hr"></div>

					<h1>
						Slide title
						<small>then a label inline</small>
					</h1>
					<p>
						<img src="/images/slides/k12lab.jpg" alt="K12lab.com" class="blockElement" />
					</p>

					<p>
						<img src="/images/slides/thoughtworks.jpg" alt="ThoughtWorks.com" class="blockElement" />
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
